CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABuildCrusaderUpdated
"USA's main battle tank. Crusader tanks are well-armored and armed with a powerful cannon. Can be upgraded with composite armor to increase their survivability. \n \nStrong vs. vehicles, buildings \n Weak vs. aircraft, missile armed infantry"
END

CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABuildPaladinUpdated
"USA's Advanced Prototype Tank. Paladin tanks are boasted with their armor and equipped with jet-assisted shells to increase their firepower. In addition, Paladin tanks are equipped with a powerful point defense laser that can be used against enemy missiles and infantry. Can be upgraded with composite armor to further increase their survivability.  \n \n Strong vs. tanks, buildings, and rockets \n Weak vs. aircraft"
END


