CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABuildRangerUpdated
"America's basic infantry with the best training. Rangers are equipped with an M16 type assault rifle and body armor. They can clear garrison buildings or groups of infantry with flash-bang grenades. \n \nStrong vs. infantry \n Weak vs. light vehicles"
END

CONTROLBAR:Lazr_ToolTipUSABuildRanger
"America's basic infantry with the best training. Laser Rangers are equipped with a laser assault rifle that can vaporize armor. They can clear garrison buildings or groups of infantry with flash-bang grenades. \n \nStrong vs. infantry, buildings \n Weak vs. aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:Lazr_ToolTipUSABuildColonelBurton
"USA's famous commando. Colonel Burton is Camouflaged. Reveals himself when he shoots or plants a bomb. He is armed with the more powerful OICW burst weapon. \n \n Build Limit: 1 \n Strong vs. Infantry \n Weak vs. Scouts, Aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:Lazr_ToolTipUSABuildComanche
"USA's primary attack helicopter: the Comanche. Fires powerful lasers and cannon. Re-arms in the air. \n \n Strong vs. tanks, light vehicles, infantry \n Weak vs. jet-fighters, missile-armed infantry, anti-air defenses"
END

