CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABuildAdvancedMicrowave
"USA's support tank that can disable buildings, vehicles, clears garrison buildings and prevents enemy infantry firing weapons when inside bunkers with a microwave beam. The heat emitter is lethal to enemy infantry when close. \n \n Strong vs. infantry, vehicles, buildings \n Weak vs. missile-armed infantry, aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABuildCIAOfficer
"A well train CIA Agents, they are armed with an advanced laser pistol that ignores armor. Equips with time and remote demo charges. \n \n Strong vs. infantry, vehicles, buildings \n Weak vs. snipers, aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:TooltipUSAUpgradeCountermeasures2
"All american aircraft gain extra armor and capable of evading 50% of missiles fired at them using flares. The flares are ineffective against anti-air small arms, lasers and gatting bullets"
END

CONTROLBAR:TooltipUSABoss_HypersonicAurora
"USA's light bomber. Hypersonic attack makes Aurora immune to enemy fire. After attack, speed is reduced to 50%. \n Equipped with a Point Defense Laser. \n \n Strong vs. buildings \n Weak vs. fighters, anti-air weapon systems"
END

CONTROLBAR:ToolTipUSABoss_BuildHypersonicFuelAirAurora
"USA's light bomber. Hypersonic attack makes Aurora immune to enemy fire while dropping a small Fuel-Air Bomb. After attack, speed is reduced to 50%. \n Equipped with a Point Defense Laser. \n \n Strong vs. buildings \n Weak vs. fighters, anti-air weapon systems"
END

