CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildCombatBikeTerrorist
"Fast and versatile. Comes with a toxin terrorist. \n \n Strong vs. buildings, infantry \n Weak vs. aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildTunnelNetwork
"Base defense and underground tunnel. Fires a stream of toxin, starts as camouflaged and arms with demolitions ability. Units can enter the Tunnel Network and exit at any other Tunnel Network."
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildTerrorist
"Suicide soldier explodes in a cloud of toxin and demolition explosives. \n \n Strong vs. tanks, buildings \n Weak vs. infantry, light vehicles, aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildToxinRebel
"Fires a stream of toxin. Arms with booby traps, Demo Charges and Demolitions Ability. Starts as camouflaged. \n \n Strong vs. infantry, buildings \n Weak vs. tanks, light vehicles"
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildBombTruck
"A suicide vehicle that can disguise to look like any vehicle friend or foe. Arms with Demolition Explosive Bomb and Bio Bomb either Anthrax Beta or Gamma. \n \n Strong vs. infantry, vehicles, buildings \n Weak vs. scouts, aircraft"
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildScudStorm
"A superweapon that launches 9 volley of SCUD missiles at a target location. The
scud missiles are fueled with more powerful explosives and toxins combined that
can destroy an enemy superweapon in a single strike
Can be camouflaged with the camo-netting upgrade. \n \n Countdown Timer: 5:00"
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildStingerSite
"GLA's Anti-air and anti-tank base defense. Comes with 3 Toxin Stinger Soldiers that can launch deadly toxins against both ground and air tagets. Starts as camouflaged and can be upgraded with demolitions ablity."
END

CONTROLBAR:GLABoss_ToolTipGLABuildStingerSoldier
"Low fire rate and long ranged Stinger Soldier with toxin homing rockets that can destroy a ballistic missile in large numbers. Starts as camouflaged. \n \n Strong vs. tanks, vehicles, aircaft \n Weak vs. snipers, artillery shells"
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildHijacker
"Hijackers are thieves that can capture any enemy vehicle. Camouflaged even when moving. \n \n Strong vs. tanks, vehicles \n Weak vs. infantry, scouts"
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildCommandCenter
"Commands special GLA powers. Trains Workers for constructing buildings or gathering supplies from a supply stash. \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting."
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildSupplyStash
"Collects supplies \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting. When upgraded, workers that gather supplies will be camouflaged."
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildBarracks
"Trains GLA soldiers \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting."
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildArmsDealer
"Builds various GLA vehicles \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting."
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildPalace
"Holds important GLA technologies and upgrades. Can be garrisoned up to 5 troops as a bunker. \n \n Gives access to advanced GLA arsenal \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting."
END

CONTROLBAR:Slth_ToolTipGLABuildBlackMarket
"Holds important GLA technologies and upgrades. Provides free supplies to the GLA player by selling resources inside. \n \n Can be upgraded with camo-netting."
END

